{"title":"【JOI2017春季合宿】Cultivation","time_limit":2000,"memory_limit":256,"url":"http://uoj.ac/problem/355","statement":[{"title":"# 题目描述","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<p>小M家有一个 $W\\times H$ 的农场。</p>\n<p>每年开春的时候，小M会在农场的 $n$ 个位置撒下种子。</p>\n<p>每天，小M可以选择一个当天的风向（东，南，西或者北），所有的种子会被风带着朝着风向移动一格。一旦一个种子在某个时刻到达了某个格子，那么之后的每个时刻这个格子都会有一个种子。</p>\n<p>最少几天小M可以把所有农场都撒上种子。</p>\n"},{"title":"# 输入格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<p>第一行两个整数 $W,H$，意义如题面所述。</p>\n<p>第二行一个整数 $n$。</p>\n<p>接下来 $n$ 行，每行两个整数 $x_i,y_i$，表示第$i$个种子的位置。</p>\n"},{"title":"# 输出格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<p>一行一个整数，表示答案。</p>\n"},{"title":"# 样例一","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<h4>input</h4>\n<pre>3 4\n3\n1 2\n1 4\n2 3\n\n</pre>\n\n<h4>output</h4>\n<pre>3\n\n</pre>\n\n"},{"title":"# 样例二","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<h4>input</h4>\n<pre>4 4\n4\n1 1\n1 4\n4 1\n4 4\n\n</pre>\n\n<h4>output</h4>\n<pre>4\n\n</pre>\n\n\n\n"},{"title":"# 限制与约定","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<p>对于所有数据，</p>\n<p>$1\\le n\\le 300,1\\le W,H\\le 10^9,1\\le x_i \\le W,1\\le y_i\\le H,(x_i,y_i)\\not=(x_j,y_j)(1\\le i &lt; j \\le n)$</p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n <table class=\"table table-bordered table-text-center table-vertical-middle\"><thead><tr><th>子任务</th>\n    <th>分值</th>\n    <th>$W$</th>\n    <th>$H$</th>\n    <th>$n$</th>\n   </tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td>\n    <td>5</td>\n    <td>$\\le 4$</td>\n    <td>$\\le 4$</td>\n    <td>无</td>\n   </tr><tr><td>2</td>\n    <td>10</td>\n    <td>$\\le 40$</td>\n    <td>$\\le 40$</td>\n    <td>无</td>\n   </tr><tr><td>3</td>\n    <td>15</td>\n    <td>$\\le 40$</td>\n    <td>无</td>\n    <td>无</td>\n   </tr><tr><td>4</td>\n    <td>30</td>\n    <td>无</td>\n    <td>无</td>\n    <td>$\\le 25$</td>\n   </tr><tr><td>5</td>\n    <td>20</td>\n    <td>无</td>\n    <td>无</td>\n    <td>$\\le 100$</td>\n   </tr><tr><td>6</td>\n    <td>20</td>\n    <td>无</td>\n    <td>无</td>\n    <td>$\\le 300$</td>\n   </tr></tbody></table></div>\n\n<p><strong>时间限制：</strong>$2\\texttt{s}$</p>\n<p><strong>空间限制：</strong>$256\\texttt{MB}$</p>\n"},{"title":"# 下载","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<p><a href=\"/download.php?type=problem&amp;id=355\">样例数据下载</a></p>\n\n"}]}